om/music/2023/dec/18/victoria-mary-clarke-on-her-husband-shane-macgowan-he-gave-up-heroin-and-our-connection-deepened">守灵会上留下 10,000 欧元</a>。</p><p>另外，The Pogues 的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/the-pogues-fairytale-of-new-york-to-be-released-on-7-inch-vinyl-for-charity-3558401">《Fairytale Of New York》将发行 7 英寸黑胶唱片，用于慈善事业</a>。</p><p>肖恩<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shane-macgowan-widow-victoria-shares-plans-book-of-unpublished-songs-3560223">·麦高恩 (Shane MacGowan) 的遗孀维多利亚 (Victoria) 分享了计划发行他“未出版”歌曲的书的帖子，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
